						               													<description>From the back of the box:&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Refreshingly different, POCKET ENIGMA is the perfect game for TWO adults.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;It's a race to the centre, BUT with a twist; you can sabotage your opponent. See them squirm as you move them back. Yes, at long last the pocket game that brings out the scoundrel in us all.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;The Riddle is the key - the NEW Challenge of the 90's. Some are easy, some fiendishly difficult. Can't solve them? Ask for a clue and see who your friends really are.&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Pocket Enigma is a small version of the Enigma game of riddles, with a small board inside the box lid, two pieces, a dice, some instructions, and 500 riddles.  The objective is to move your gaming piece through a maze, from a starting point on the outer edge of the board, to the finishing point, at the center of the board. Players take it in turns to roll a die and move their pawn the indicated number of spaces along the track. There are special spaces along the track where a player is asked to solve a riddle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
